title: Harry Edison Quartet - Complete Sweets At The Haig (1953)
description:
HARRY EDISON QUARTET - The Complete Unedited "Sweets At The Haig" 1953 Recordings

(New Rip + Scans)

A collection of live performances recorded at The Haig, Hollywood, July 1, 1953

Harry "Sweets" Edison - trumpet
Arnold Ross - piano
Joe Comfort - bass
Alvin Stoller - drums

1. September In The Rain [6:32]
2. 'S Wonderful [3:54]
3. Just You, Just Me [3:51]
4. Indiana [5:44]
5. Pennies From Heaven [6:18]
6. These Foolish Things [7:23]
7. Tea For Two [6:58]

2003 Fresh Sound
